text: Ahmed Ragab (born 29 September 1991) is an Egyptian competitive sailor. He competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in Rio de Janeiro, in the men's Laser class. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Egyptian male sailors (sport) Category:Olympic sailors of Egypt Category:Sailors at the 2016 Summer Olympics – Laser
